data.description: Welcome home to this one of a kind property! This massive home sits on a little over 8 acres in Doylestown. You will notice the open floor plan when you walk in the front door leading to a large dining room.  To the left there is a mud room, half bath, and laundry room for 1st floor convenience.  The fully applianced eat in kitchen has new cabinets, countertops and much more including an island that has built in electric The first floor also offers a main floor owners suite complete with full attached bath and walk-in closet. Upstairs you will find 4 additional oversized bedrooms and the 2nd full bathroom.  Head to the partially finished walk-out basement to see the theater/rec room.  Walking out the basement door you come across a very large 3200 sq/ft outbuilding that can house 8 cars, has heat, and an office with heat/AC and an additional bathroom. The potential for this home is endless.  The seller has completely redone and remodified the floor plan over the past two years, and you can find an entire page-long list of improvements in the supplements.  This home has well, Oversized septic with two tanks, and another well that has the potential to be hooked up. You truly will not find another home like this! Some recent updates within the past 4 years are new roof, hot water tank (2/17/24), heat pump, furnace, and A/C.  The "big" stuff is all done it just needs your personal touch!  Call today for a private showing!
